    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your<strong> vegetable</strong> <strong>stock</strong> <strong>mix</strong> and <strong>Dijon mustard</strong> in 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[450ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml] </span><strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water </strong>and 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>milk</strong> – this is your <strong>creamy veg stock</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into small bite-sized pieces</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
