        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are fork-tender, add your <strong>salmon flakes</strong>, <strong>capers</strong>, most of the <strong>chopped dill </strong>(save some for garnish!) and <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>spinach </strong>to the pan</p><p>Add <strong>half</strong> your <strong>soured cream </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>Scandi-style salmon & dill chowder</strong></p>",
