    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Scandi-style salmon & dill chowder</strong> and top with the <strong>ciabatta croutons</strong></p><p>Dollop over the <strong>remaining soured cream </strong>and garnish with the <strong>remaining chopped dill</strong></p><p>Season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
